app_name: Groups Control Groups Messenger Apps Grapherex Secure Messenger
app_description: Grapherex is the app with secure messenger cryptocurrency wallet and many other useful features. Secure Messenger It s a really simple and convenient way to send text messages voice messages photos videos stickers files and even money. Also you have to know that you use it with end to end encryption. Ohh! It means that you can send information highly secure. Simple free You can register simply with your phone number integrate your contacts book and start messaging straight away. Call Video Voice and video calls take advantage of the same end to end encryption that is used for messaging and multimedia sharing. Your voice and video calls are always private and work without the server but on a peer to peer basis. Cryptocurrency wallet Open a single cryptocurrency wallet to safely store send and receive crypto currency with Grapherex right on your device. Only you hold the private key and can access your account. Your data and funds are protected by E2E encryption and state of art information security technologies.
